    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so annoying to spend time at the urgent care for something that's probably just a bruise or a minor ligament thing. i've done RICE before and it worked fine. do you really think i need to go in if i can just manage the pain with some ibuprofen and keep it elevated for the weekend? it doesn't feel like a \"broken\" kind of pain, just a really bad ache.",
